name: Moderniui-ios
tagline: A project to update iUi to modern versions of iOS.
body:
# ModerniUi-iOS
ModerniUI-iOS is a updated version of iUI, the update was created to make creating web apps easier. 
</br>
iUI is a great framework but sadly, no longer updated. This was created for people who enjoy the framework, and want to see it come back.
</br>
It currently isn't a fork of iUI so the user will have to modify a version of iUI 0.4.1 themselves, you can also use the installer if you are on Linux or Mac!
